Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:33.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}人类动物园，我不敢相信居然还存在\N{\fnArial\fs32}The Human Zoo. I can't believe it still exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:34.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸肯定在里面\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad's got to be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:37.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们只要找到他并将他救出来\N{\fnArial\fs32}We just have to find him and bust him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:48.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那些宝石人\N{\fnArial\fs32}Those Gems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶守卫\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethyst guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:51.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:52.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好像我们能大摇大摆的走进去\N{\fnArial\fs32}Like we could just waltz up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.85,0:00:55.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一个无主的珍珠，一个融合体，\N{\fnArial\fs32}as an ownerless Pearl, a Fusion,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.52,0:00:57.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}和-和，你\N{\fnArial\fs32}and -- and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:01:01.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们只需要伪装，我就叫“艾斯呆板·宇宙老爹”\N{\fnArial\fs32}We just need disguises. I'll be Esteban Universedad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:04.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，你的名字并没有用\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, it doesn't matter what your name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.29,0:01:06.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们太显眼了\N{\fnArial\fs32}We're all going to stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不会\N{\fnArial\fs32}We won't stand out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.95,0:01:11.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}只要我们的表现与本来的身份一致的话\N{\fnArial\fs32}if we play the roles we were made for.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.90,0:01:13.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}红宝石！蓝宝石！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ruby! Sapphire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.64,0:01:16.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好吧，各位，听她的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay everybody, hear her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:20.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}今天，我，作为蓝宝石，正在执行公务，伴随我的有红宝石护卫...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Today, I'm a Sapphire traveling with my Ruby guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:20.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.94,0:01:22.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还有我个人的珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs32}And my personal Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.78,0:01:24.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Mm-hmm!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.01,0:01:27.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}艾斯呆板，我将你作为献给动物园的大礼\N{\fnArial\fs32}Esteban, I've brought you as an offering for the zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.72,0:01:30.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}“可怜的艾斯呆板啊！”\N{\fnArial\fs32}{\i1}Pobrecito Esteban!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:31.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，我呢？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, what about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.45,0:01:34.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你作为额外打手陪同我\N{\fnArial\fs32}You're accompanying me as extra muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:35.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}像她们那种？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Muscle like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:37.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没错\N{\fnArial\fs32}Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:40.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但我从没看见过其他紫晶\N{\fnArial\fs32}But I've never even seen another Amethyst before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:43.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那我做什么？如果我说错话了呢？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What do I do? What if I say something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:44.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}看着办吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}Just look the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:46.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你too young，我们长者\N{\fnArial\fs32}You're new and we're rusty,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:49.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们只用坚持到找到格雷格就行\N{\fnArial\fs32}but we just have to sell this long enough to find Greg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.57,0:01:51.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这真的管用吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Is this really going to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:52.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}不\N{\fnArial\fs32}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.61,0:01:53.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃？-呃...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh? - Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们得呆在一起，直截了当\N{\fnArial\fs32}Just stick together, play it straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:59.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}让我们改变未来\N{\fnArial\fs32}Let's change the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:05.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们永远不可能关住我的，你们这群石头蛋！\N{\fnArial\fs32}You'll never cage me, ya rock heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:13.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}说明来意\N{\fnArial\fs32}State your purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:16.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我是来完成动物园的货运任务的\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm here to make a delivery to the Human Zoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:20.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}坏消息-人类动物园关闭了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Bad news -- the Human Zoo shut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:25.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也就是意味着我们不得不把你直接扔进太空\N{\fnArial\fs32}which means we'll just have to throw you into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:29.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哈！看，他居然信了\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ha! Look. It believed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.55,0:02:34.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们在干吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.98,0:02:38.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没什么，霍利蓝玛瑙-没什么，霍利蓝玛瑙\N{\fnArial\fs32}Nothing, Holly Blue Agate. Nothing, Holly Blue Agate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:44.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}为什么你不告诉我\N{\fnArial\fs32}Why didn't you tell me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}蓝宝石来这里了？\N{\fnArial\fs32}there was a Sapphire here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:48.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你对她说了什么不敬的话吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What have you miscreants been saying to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:49.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没有，长官\N{\fnArial\fs32}Nothing, Holly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你一定要见谅啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}You'll have to forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:53.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}他们来自地球\N{\fnArial\fs32}They're from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:56.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}咳！道歉\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ahem! Apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.24,0:02:57.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}请原谅我们-请原谅我们\N{\fnArial\fs32}Forgive us. Forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗷！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}请原谅我们，###-请原谅我们，###\N{\fnArial\fs32}Forgive us, Your Clarity. Forgive us, Your Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}没必要再揪着旧事不放\N{\fnArial\fs32}No use dwelling on the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我为收藏集合带来了一个新的人类\N{\fnArial\fs32}I've brought a new human for the collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这多么新奇啊-\N{\fnArial\fs32}How unprecedented --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:09.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一千年来什么都出现\N{\fnArial\fs32}nothing for millennia
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:11.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而现在突然两个人类接踵而至！\N{\fnArial\fs32}and then two humans back-to-back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:13.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也许，这样最好吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}Well, it's probably for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.49,0:03:15.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}第一个的状态...并不好\N{\fnArial\fs32}That first one wasn't in the...best condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸！那是他！-嘘！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad! That's him! - Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:22.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，人类无尽无休的叫唤！他在说什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, they're incessant barking! What is it saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:25.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}-另一个也很吵\N{\fnArial\fs32}- The other one was loud too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而且还在不停挣扎\N{\fnArial\fs32}And all that thrashing about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:32.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很确定蓝钻石愿意亲自表达谢意\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'm sure Blue Diamond will want to thank you personally,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:34.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但你刚好错过她了\N{\fnArial\fs32}but you just missed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶，带这个人类去-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethyst, take this human to the --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}等等！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}有件事，我们走了那么远\N{\fnArial\fs32}The thing is we've traveled so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:43.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果就这么离开实在是可惜\N{\fnArial\fs32}and it would be a shame to leave so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也许你能带我们参观一下设施？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Perhaps you'd grant us a tour of the facility?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我非常荣幸\N{\fnArial\fs32}I would be honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.06,0:03:50.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}来这里，###\N{\fnArial\fs32}Right this way, Your Grand Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:53.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}紫晶得留在这里看门\N{\fnArial\fs32}Amethysts are to stay and guard the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，但...\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.20,0:03:56.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}大门\N{\fnArial\fs32}The door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.14,0:04:06.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你的珍珠总是与您肩并肩行走吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Does your Pearl always walk next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:10.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我在这就好\N{\fnArial\fs32}I'll just be right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.25,0:04:12.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}嗯，很健谈嘛\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hmm. Chatty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}此设施原来属于粉钻石\N{\fnArial\fs32}This facility originally belonged to Pink Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:19.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}收留并任用本来毫无用处的石英们\N{\fnArial\fs32}and houses and staffs the otherwise useless Quartzes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:21.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那些石英制造于她的殖民地\N{\fnArial\fs32}she produced on what was her colony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:25.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但蓝钻石与她值得信赖的玛瑙-\N{\fnArial\fs32}But Blue Diamond and her trusted Agate --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}也就是我-\N{\fnArial\fs32}that's me --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:29.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}从第二代出现后一直在维护这个地方\N{\fnArial\fs32}have been maintaining this place since the dawn of Era 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是她要做什么，还是我要先说什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Is she going to do it, or should I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:38.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.47,0:04:39.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}珍珠，门\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pearl, the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:40.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hm? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.68,0:04:42.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好，好\N{\fnArial\fs32}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我知道了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你对她真是有耐心啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}You are so patient with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:49.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你是如何做到的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}How do you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.99,0:04:53.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}作为蓝宝石，我知道这肯定会发生的\N{\fnArial\fs32}As a Sapphire, I know it will happen eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}就这样吧\N{\fnArial\fs32}That will be all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:02.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}坚持一下\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:05.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}跟上啊，珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs32}Do keep up, Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:06.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃\N{\fnArial\fs32}Ugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:10.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这个设施的下半部分\N{\fnArial\fs32}The bottom half of this structure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:13.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}完全关注于物种保存\N{\fnArial\fs32}is devoted entirely to specimen containment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:16.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}显然，人类不愿意被拘禁\N{\fnArial\fs32}Apparently, humans don't take well to captivity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但只要你了解他们的需求\N{\fnArial\fs32}But once you understand their needs,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:21.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}他们很容易控制\N{\fnArial\fs32}they're easy to control.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:24.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这真是个悲剧-粉钻在宇宙中的存在\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's tragic that Pink Diamond's existence in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}居然如此有限\N{\fnArial\fs32}ended up being so finite.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:29.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但蓝钻的表现是如此无私，\N{\fnArial\fs32}But what a selfless act for Blue Diamond
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:32.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}愿意站出来花费自己的时间与精力\N{\fnArial\fs32}to step forward and spend her own time and energy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}保存这个地方-只为纪念粉钻石\N{\fnArial\fs32}preserving this place in Pink Diamond's memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:38.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这是蓝钻石仁慈与友爱\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's a real testament to Blue Diamond's merciful
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:41.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}真正的纪念碑，你不觉得吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}and giving nature, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:43.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃，当然\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:45.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Argh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}坚持住，红宝石，我们的角色，记得吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hold it together, Ruby. Our roles, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:49.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}一定要“艾斯呆板”住啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Gotta Esteban it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:52.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}而这里，显然，是人类放置滑槽\N{\fnArial\fs32}And here, of course, is the human disposal chute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:53.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如-如何进入动物园？\N{\fnArial\fs32}H-How do get in the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:58.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，又是那滑稽的噪音\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, there it goes again with its hilarious noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.19,0:06:00.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}那么，你是如何进入动物园的？\N{\fnArial\fs32}So, how do you get in the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.19,0:06:03.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}非常好的问题，###\N{\fnArial\fs32}Excellent question, Your Grand Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:05.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}在一些特别情况下\N{\fnArial\fs32}On the rare occasion that we would need
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们进入收容区域\N{\fnArial\fs32}to enter the containment area,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:09.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}要通过这个维护大门\N{\fnArial\fs32}we would do so via this service door.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:12.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爸爸，这个门是我们找到爸爸的关键\N{\fnArial\fs32}Dad. That door's how we get to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:14.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们只需要分散一下注意力\N{\fnArial\fs32}We just need to come up with a distraction.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.07,0:06:15.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好的！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:18.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}作为单向接入点，这里并没有发生逃脱的可能性\N{\fnArial\fs32}As one-way access point, there are no risks of an escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.51,0:06:21.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}实际上，只有一次这里被用于一个人类-\N{\fnArial\fs32}In fact, it's only been used once for a human --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:22.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}爆炸！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}呃\N{\fnArial\fs32}Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:28.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我刚想起来我忘了关掉引力引擎了\N{\fnArial\fs32}I just remembered I left the gravity engine idling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:32.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}对不起，蓝宝石，我真是健忘和无用啊\N{\fnArial\fs32}Sorry, my Sapphire, I'm so forgetful and disposable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:33.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}...是一个我预见到的事件\N{\fnArial\fs32}...a foreseen turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:42.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}是的，它将会过热并爆炸\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, it is going to overheat and explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:44.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}破坏会非常巨大\N{\fnArial\fs32}The damage will be massive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}###\N{\fnArial\fs32}My word!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:47.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我不知道为什么有人会将宇宙飞船托付给红宝石\N{\fnArial\fs32}I don't know why anyone trusts Rubies with those ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:49.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这就是后果\N{\fnArial\fs32}This is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.27,0:06:51.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}如果我们抓紧，我们能关掉引擎\N{\fnArial\fs32}If we hurry, we can disable the engine
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.81,0:06:53.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}避免任何破坏\N{\fnArial\fs32}before any damage is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我应该只要五分钟\N{\fnArial\fs32}I should only take five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}所以每个人要做到行为规矩\N{\fnArial\fs32}so everyone be on your best behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}来这里，###\N{\fnArial\fs32}This way, Your Clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.05,0:07:08.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}虽然，我确定你不需要我的指引\N{\fnArial\fs32}Although, I'm sure you don't need my guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:09.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Argh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:11.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我才不信\N{\fnArial\fs32}I can't believe all that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:13.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}蓝宝石有那么仁慈！\N{\fnArial\fs32}about Blue Diamond being merciful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她会粉碎宝石啊！\N{\fnArial\fs32}She's a shatterer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:18.43,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}她对蓝宝石大喊大叫！她憎恨融合！\N{\fnArial\fs32}She yelled at Sapphire! She hates Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还有爱！\N{\fnArial\fs32}And love!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:22.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我知道，红宝石，但我们并没有多少时间了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I know, Ruby, but we don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:23.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们得打开这道门！\N{\fnArial\fs32}We have to open this door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好，好\N{\fnArial\fs32}Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:25.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}珍珠，开门！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Pearl, open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}当然，我还会做什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Of course. What else am I good for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}这个和其他的不一样\N{\fnArial\fs32}It's different than the other ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}\N{\fnArial\fs32}Aha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:44.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我其实根本理解不了这个\N{\fnArial\fs32}I actually can't figure this out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.59,0:07:45.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}什么？！\N{\fnArial\fs32}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:48.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}但珍珠，你是团队里的骇客\N{\fnArial\fs32}But Pearl, you're our hacker.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我们没那么多时间！\N{\fnArial\fs32}We don't have time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}史蒂文，帮我打开门！\N{\fnArial\fs32}Steven, help me open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:51.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}好的\N{\fnArial\fs32}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}还有，珍珠，骇得快点！\N{\fnArial\fs32}And Pearl, hack faster!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:03.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我很高兴我们马上就回来了！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I am so glad we're almost back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.75,0:08:06.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}我真的很享受这次行程！\N{\fnArial\fs32}I was really enjoying the tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:09.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}使得，我能从你的声音里听出来\N{\fnArial\fs32}Yes, I can tell by the tone of your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.52,0:08:13.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}再次感谢你避免了这次危机\N{\fnArial\fs32}Thank you so much again for averting that crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:17.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}发生了什么？\N{\fnArial\fs32}What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.46,0:08:19.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}哦，呃，我确定这有合理的解释-\N{\fnArial\fs32}Oh, well, I'm sure there's a reasonable --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs42}你们看到是哪个紫晶做的吗？\N{\fnArial\fs32}Did you see the Amethyst that did this?
